  "detailed_description": "<br><br>Trip Not is a physics-driven, parkour Platformer. Meat colorful Character along the way up, each step accompanied by whimsical voice acting. Watch out, though, Every platform is a dynamic physics challenge, Unlike other games in the genre, you have safe points. Perfect for speed runs<br><br>Meet Kevin a poor fish face, out of water seeking his place in the world. Convinced that dreams come true in the fantastical fun-land, he sets out to discover where he truly belongs, striving to shed his weirdness. Collect money along the way, then he is flat broke, and no one is going to employ someone with his face.<br>What does he find in they end, and can his stupid face be restored?<br><br>Meet characters along the way<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703810/extras/18bb2a72d2e2b1202e0fdd6140c9524f.poster.avif?t=1704050122\" width=480 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703810/extras/18bb2a72d2e2b1202e0fdd6140c9524f.webm?t=1704050122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2703810/extras/18bb2a72d2e2b1202e0fdd6140c9524f.mp4?t=1704050122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
